Texts.Chs: 布莱特夫人在她任职大守护者时优雅肖像。我不明白他们为什么选择不展示它。
Texts.Eng: A graceful portrait of Madame Bright in her Grand Protector days. Why they chose not to display it is beyond me.

Texts.Chs: 前大守护者艾斯特·布莱特的肖像。
Texts.Eng: A portrait of former Grand Protector Esther Bright.

Texts.Chs: 嘿，那是布莱特夫人！这个怎么样。
Texts.Eng: Hey now - that's missus Bright! How 'bout that.

Texts.Chs: 我说...那是布莱特夫人吗？
Texts.Eng: I say... Is that Madame Bright?

Texts.Chs: 是布莱特夫人！我在学院的时候从没见过她的这张肖像。
Texts.Eng: It's Lady Bright! I've never seen this portrait of her back at the academy.

Texts.Chs: 布莱特夫人在这上面看起来很很很年轻。这幅画肯肯肯定很老了。
Texts.Eng: Ms. Bright looks sso young here... Painting musst be old.

Texts.Chs: 埃丝特·布莱特夫人，在年轻时的大守护者肖像。
Texts.Eng: Ms. Esther Bright, in her youthful Grand Protector days.

Texts.Chs: 以前从没见过布莱特女士的这幅画像。哦，嘿！那是同一棵学院的树！
Texts.Eng: Never seen this portrait of Ms. Bright before... Oh hey! That's the same tree from the academy!
